{"tid":477881,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"【月經】放低你覺得陳奕迅最正嘅十首歌同原因","createTime":"2017-11-23T12:47:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-23T13:32:28.000Z","uid":48498,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"14001c448da16b8c8fbd226e4c6bc234490e6df5","tid":477881,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:47:40.000Z","msg":"1st<br />\n我的快樂時代<br />\n2nd<br />\n我甚麼都沒有<br />\n3rd<br />\n與我同在<br />\n4th<br />\n不來也不去<br />\n5th<br />\n月球上的人<br />\n6th<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n7th<br />\n天公地道<br />\n8th<br />\nK歌之王<br />\n9th<br />\n人來人往<br />\n10th<br />\n幸災樂禍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯，交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e62c6570ad68ded7525cd06f41612c288be1aa1","tid":477881,"uid":48498,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:51:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1st<br />\n我的快樂時代<br />\n2nd<br />\n我甚麼都沒有<br />\n3rd<br />\n與我同在<br />\n4th<br />\n不來也不去<br />\n5th<br />\n月球上的人<br />\n6th<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n7th<br />\n天公地道<br />\n8th<br />\nK歌之王<br />\n9th<br />\n人來人往<br />\n10th<br />\n幸災樂禍<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不服來辯，交流下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我自己覺得我的快樂時代，我甚麼都沒有同與我同在好似三部曲，由執著到接受到睇化過程，係林夕好神好有深度嘅作品，值得慢慢品嘗，唔同年紀聽會有唔同嘅睇法。<br />\n<br />\n就連單春自己唱都有因為自己嘅年紀歷練而有唔同嘅感覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對比起所謂嘅病態三部曲，意味深遠好多"},{"pid":"ddd8ef959547633c448ab9385abbb312501f04ea","tid":477881,"uid":134747,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:54:20.000Z","msg":"綿綿<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n傷信<br />\n抱擁這分鐘<br />\n愈想愈無謂<br />\n防不勝防<br />\n阿牛<br />\nKatrina<br />\n原來這裡沒有你<br />\n時光倒流二十年<br />\n<br />\n排名不分先後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ed0ccfd19e3f1c6fe1bb6e4ad23faf676c72889","tid":477881,"uid":76249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:55:14.000Z","msg":"開不了心"},{"pid":"ef83d5489f267b1c996bdcee0114f72e96b515ce","tid":477881,"uid":48498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:56:25.000Z","msg":"之後到不來也不去，當中玩字固之然係林夕巔峰時期嘅產物。而固中嘅意思亦都充滿佛理，每個人都係本來無一物，從來冇得亦都冇失，咁又何必要記住呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f8722a65db48230828af1d3a6b002dd6c650b12","tid":477881,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>開不了心</blockquote><br />\n我睇完inside Out 即刻就諗起依首歌，用短短幾分鐘講一個道理其實真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"471c71ff0d528ef7d67e76c19e683a5119a05dc0","tid":477881,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T12:59:34.000Z","msg":"只有《六月飛霜》同《苦瓜》曾經派台到亞視<br />\n<br />\n所以樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30232d7f66286c7aa0ce4342b92f98b5a6c9460b","tid":477881,"uid":48498,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:00:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>只有《六月飛霜》同《苦瓜》曾經派台到亞視<br />\n<br />\n所以樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7bd484acfb6d0c34cab8c22c2029cffa9bc40ae8","tid":477881,"uid":76249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:01:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>開不了心</blockquote><br />\n我睇完inside Out 即刻就諗起依首歌，用短短幾分鐘講一個道理其實真係好難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n呢首歌有種吸引力"},{"pid":"4a3a6d441140adbee8fcfb4bc715dc5d56015b74","tid":477881,"uid":134747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-23T13:32:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>綿綿<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n原來這裡沒有你<br />\n時光倒流二十年<br />\n<br />\n排名不分先後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n而四首歌係我覺得Eason唱得好溫柔嘅幾首歌<br />\n綿綿係編曲上真係做得好靚<br />\n彈過佢嘅intro 同 chord ，感覺好似有人同你講故事咁<br />\n／<br />\n黑暗中漫舞<br />\n歌詞結構好工整，加上佢係對稱每一句<br />\n聽落好似聽一首詩<br />\n／<br />\n原來這裡沒有你<br />\n一開始覺得副歌嘅節奏好順<br />\n聽聽下，就終於咗而首<br />\n／<br />\n時光倒流二十年<br />\n低音高音轉換好舒服"}]}